OL,3,CAre children with allergies at risk in
OL,4,CScottish schools?
OL,6,FNew research has highlighted a
OL,7,F"postcode lottery" that leaves pupils
OL,8,Fwith severe allergies dangerously
OL,9,Fexposed.
OL,11,FThe Benedict Blythe Foundation has
OL,12,Ffound that fewer than 1 in 10 schools
OL,13,Fin Scotland hold a spare allergy pen
OL,14,Fadrenaline auto-injector (AAI) for
OL,15,Femergency use.
OL,17,FWhen it comes to training, around two-
OL,18,Fthirds of schools provide this for
OL,19,Fstaff with almost half of Scottish
OL,20,Fschools having no formal allergy
OL,21,Fpolicy.
