OL,3,CAre children with allergies at risk in
OL,4,CScottish schools?
OL,6,FThe data was gathered by the family of
OL,7,Fa five-year-old Benedict Blythe, who
OL,8,Fdied after a severe reaction to cow's
OL,9,Fmilk at school. His family are now
OL,10,Fcalling for a new law to ensure every
OL,11,Fschool has a clear allergy plan in
OL,12,Fplace.
OL,14,FHelen and Peter Blythe have been
OL,15,Fcampaigning in England, Northern
OL,16,FIreland and now Scotland for new
OL,17,Fsafety improvements.
