OL,3,CAre children with allergies at risk in
OL,4,CScottish schools?
OL,6,F"Every day, children with life-
OL,7,Fthreatening allergies go to school in
OL,8,FScotland without guaranteed
OL,9,Fprotection,"Jsaid Helen Blythe, co-
OL,10,Ffounder of the Benedict Blythe
OL,11,FFoundation with her husband Peter.
OL,13,F"These findings show that despite the
OL,14,Fbest efforts of individual schools,
OL,15,Fthere is no consistent system or legal
OL,16,Fframework to keep them safe.
OL,18,F"No parent should have to rely on luck
OL,19,Fwhen their child's life is at stake."
