OL,3,CAre children with allergies at risk in
OL,4,CScottish schools?
OL,6,FWe spoke to a mother from Annan, who
OL,7,Fhas a one year old child who has
OL,8,Fallergies.
OL,10,FHayley Nicholson's son is still a few
OL,11,Fyears away from entering a primary
OL,12,Fschool, but her son's medical needs
OL,13,Fare already at the front of her mind.
OL,15,FShe said: "You want them to have
OL,16,Fcooked meals at school. You don't want
OL,17,Fto have a packed lunch every day, it's
OL,18,Fa worry that they may contain
OL,19,Fsomething Jesse can't have.
