OL,3,CAre children with allergies at risk in
OL,4,CScottish schools?
OL,6,F"I never thought twice about allergies
OL,7,Fbefore having my children and seeing
OL,8,Fthem so sensitive and how they react
OL,9,Fand how it upsets them, I know it is
OL,10,Fnot anaphylactic as we know."
OL,12,F"I thought it was normal. Every school
OL,13,Fhad a pen, and were taught how to
OL,14,Frespond to allergies. There's always
OL,15,Fthat chance of what if something bad
OL,16,Fdid happen and the school didn't have
OL,17,Fanything to cater to this child for
OL,18,Fhaving a reaction."
