OL,3,CAre children with allergies at risk in
OL,4,CScottish schools?
OL,6,FA Scottish Government spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "To support schools, the
OL,8,FScottish Government has issued
OL,9,Fnational guidance which provides
OL,10,Finformation on ensuring the safety of
OL,11,Fpupils with food allergies and on the
OL,12,Fuse of adrenaline auto-injectors. It
OL,13,Falso makes clear that schools must
OL,14,Farrange specialist training for staff
OL,15,Fwhere a pupil has been diagnosed as
OL,16,Fbeing at risk of anaphylaxis."
